dialogue.text: This should be the right building. It looks pretty tall though. You ready, Boyfriend?
Beep!
The bluetooth speakers should be connected now...
hm?..
Oh! Hey guys! Over here! You're just in time!
I'm so happy you made it here! It's been 5 years since I last saw you, broski!
It's surely something that we met again in Splatoon 2 the other day.
Beep!
So you must be Dracobot.
Yup! And you must be Girlfriend.
Yeah! It's nice to meet you.
The pleasure is all mine! BF was telling me about you earlier while we were planning to have a rap battle here.
What happened to you guys 5 years ago? I don't remember seeing you there.
Well I usually wait for him near the store so he can help me with some music stuff that I wanted to do.
Though he never told me he was gonna drop out so after a couple of days of him not coming over to the store.
I stopped going there. Then I had to go back to Kreads days after that happened.
Surprised he didn't mention you during his time at high school.
He did tell me about you though. You're quite lucky to have him.
Thanks!
...Hey? Why is there body tape near the air vents?
Oh. I don't know honestly. It's been there longer than I can remember.
What about the pair of shoes with a note on it? Did a murder-suicide occur here?
I don't know about that either. Sorry... I'm honestly surprised it's still there though.
Ah...
Anyways, enough stalling! Let's get started, shall we?
Ske-be!
